Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:51.53,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你用双耳 独自聆听着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:01:04.38,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我的眼睛 映照出久远的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:07.73,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选择什么 放弃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.94,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我如何能 自行定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:14.15,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选取之物 早已在心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.08,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}向神问询 是否有误
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:20.20,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实不曾孤独过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:22.75,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实一直在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:29.82,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}现在 伸出手去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:33.06,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}已经无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:36.57,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}哪怕化身怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:44.65,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我一定 会做到
