Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:53.44,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\be2\pos(1796,276)}新加坡国际机场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.96,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}此行的目的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.59,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.01,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.11,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}请给我…列表
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得先找探索能力者来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问问首领吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:32.31,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be2\pos(1796,266)}菲律宾 市区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这辆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…到底有怎样的能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.61,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}动一动 就着火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:02.95,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你是首领？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:04.87,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.79,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}特殊能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.67,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}为什么我不能读心了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.13,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}为什么我不能读…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.84,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}他偷了我的能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.76,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}正确！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这能力真方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:29.89,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我问你 你是怎么寻找能力者的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:33.40,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不要想…不要想…不要想…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杰洛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠他找能力者是么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.28,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.16,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}开门！给我开门！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.85,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你是安杰洛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.05,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.51,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}找我干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.73,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}能力是种病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.19,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}别再用能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.28,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看地图就行了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能完美感知能力者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:42.90,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,284)}南非共和国 北部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b0\fs50\fsp0\shad0\blur2}Earlier this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b0\fs50\fsp0\shad0\blur2}the UN...said that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b0\fs50\fsp0\shad0\blur2}the Democratic Revolutionary Army
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b0\fs50\fsp0\shad0\blur2}an organization placing various kinds of danger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b0\fs50\fsp0\shad0\blur2}has been coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b0\fs50\fsp0\shad0\blur2}The UN chairman Brian Jackson
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b0\fs50\fsp0\shad0\blur2}reported that a young...少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b0\fs50\fsp0\shad0\blur2}…兵不血刃地俘虏了所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b0\fs50\fsp0\shad0\blur2}今后对残存兵力…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b0\fs50\fsp0\shad0\blur2}…争取早日和平解决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这种能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的地方在召集能力者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:27.28,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,268)}埃及 市区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.69,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小心独眼死神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独…独眼死神！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这外号好丢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会安在我头上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的感觉…是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经能知道夺到什么能力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又夺走了一个国家里的能力 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有了翻译能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有不用睡觉也能活动的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可别太勉强自己了 有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要抓紧弄完下一个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不等人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对 任务艰巨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着你的能力还在 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让病加重的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.85,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be2\pos(1796,446)}阿富汗 山区
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是个能力者聚集区
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让孩子们做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一边只有一个亮点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？没有浮现印象？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么设施？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,携带者？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经感染 但还没有显现能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是携带者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没显现就没法掠夺…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊能力是一种病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须在下一波粒子到来前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给全世界的人注射疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让能力这种病加重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力显现之后 就能掠夺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在我走后不再出现能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还得掠夺携带者才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:24.21,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,164)}印度 东部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打空弹匣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:54.20,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,167)}秘鲁共和国 郊外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 治愈能力是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 即使你在用它行善
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必须夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我把手放在右眼上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能取回时光回溯能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳或许就有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夺取能力 并不是为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再违背人之常理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打造出没有能力者的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的使命 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:57.80,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,285)}古巴共和国 市区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是敌人么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…我的敌人吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…冷静…冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能杀任何人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.53,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\be2\pos(1796,231)}沙特阿拉伯 西部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:59.57,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…声称 已抓获首都的哈桑·玛斯尔市长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.82,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府发言人表示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:06.09,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政变团伙从昨日起进攻市长官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:09.03,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市长或因此而遭俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.03,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据政府统计 在此次攻击中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:14.87,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少有十人丧生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:18.02,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十人受伤 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要去这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔…哪怕用强制手段…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得…睡会儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要…让身体歇歇…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…今日凌晨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政变的主谋 莫森·宾·亚利托
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣布无条件投降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:30.69,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从去年起在首都进行的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:34.05,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多由以孩童为主的组织进行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.48,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:39.81,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织在不明势力的打击下损失惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:42.11,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:48.82,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外界普遍认为莫森…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:52.29,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后 政府将如何应对…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:55.42,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,176)}意大利 南部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…在这里干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在战场上？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.34,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.17,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我有个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要夺取全世界的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回到她的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她 是…谁来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是个很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却想不起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:02.40,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,169)}俄罗斯联邦 市区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 爆破能力者会出现在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 你就是那个死神么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就和我们的理念一起去死…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量只会让人不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.91,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be2\pos(1796,280)}英国 市区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:34.10,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,225)}西西里 市区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…死神？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…我是死神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.74,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,492)}纽约州 曼哈顿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 我是死神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:11.76,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\be2\pos(1796,114)}亚利桑那州 郊外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种麻烦事 到底是谁想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要我来干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来个人替我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵整个地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是神 我来决定一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…我会后悔自己踢它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…会为此哭泣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还得继续努力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:53.03,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,164)}西伯利亚地区 伊尔库茨克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 死神来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:05.71,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,225)}柬埔寨 南部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:24.23,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be2\pos(1796,121)}土耳其北部 研究基地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么打不到他？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是怪物么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是独眼死神 肯定打不过的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下搞定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…这可是RPG啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.90,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\be2\pos(1796,282)}澳大利亚 东南部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于干掉传说中的死神了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许欺负弱者！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么欺负弱者…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这家伙是谁么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以做这种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙身上有巨额悬赏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他能拿很多钱！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只能让你也吃点苦头了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我绝对不会动半步！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 最后一个能力者的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「勇气」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是勇而无谋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个很有勇气的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我去求救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照约定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 就得回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完了 就得回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去…回哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像这么…约定过…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就能玩一辈子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋 咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你履行了约定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是静养一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}居然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}想想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}夺取了成千上万的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}大脑的负担一定很重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}还能说话就不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}是你的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}恋人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}我没见过你啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}真伤人…心比预想中更疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}我伤了你的心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}要知道 我们曾在同一个班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}在学生会里 一起度过高中时代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}你和我约好了要做恋人 然后才离开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}抱歉 我什么都想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}这些单词卡 是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}你直到最后都带着它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}它对你有帮助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}这是…你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}这就像我的护身符一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}一直舍不得丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}明明这么破旧 都快烂掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}谢谢…你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}如果是它帮你回到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}又让你伤心了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}不 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}只有开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}我不太懂 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}你别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}止不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)\fad(0,1200)}（我回来了）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}乙坂有宇 欢迎你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}这部摄像机 一直用来拍我不想拍的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}但从今以后 我要用它来拍大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}拍幸福的日常 一直拍下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}所以 把许许多多的幸福回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}装进这里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.83,0:23:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}能把我也拍进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}嗯 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}我该说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}说出你心里想的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}很期待今后的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}对 一切从今天起步！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}是这样的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}从今以后 让人生充满快乐吧
