Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}What the hell is hidden inside there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Treasure island we see over there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Sinking ships that come their way
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}But life has just been like that always
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}The things we have wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Are always beyond ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}They're always laughing at us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Showing off their sharpened fangs
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}We would probably be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:14:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Better off not knowing anything at all
