Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:09.70,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}这样的愿望 你我来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.71,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}也或许无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:18.63,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}只要有你在 不实现也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:25.41,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}能相伴度日 我便已满足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:45.19,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}过去的你我 有些异于常人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:50.22,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}如今依旧是异类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:21:04.20,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}让坏家伙们 闭上他们的嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:13.53,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}曾经的日子里 重复着这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:20.24,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}总是在乱来 总是在勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:26.98,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}这些回忆 也不算太差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:34.42,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}悠然的日子 静静地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:40.30,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}这样的愿望 你我来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:43.38,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}也或许无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:49.26,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}只希望我的 那一声表白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:56.75,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}他日能收获 美好的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:04.45,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}悠然的风儿 静静地吹拂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:10.54,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}风中的春天 是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:13.45,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}心中期盼着归去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:16.48,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}却已想不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:22.63,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}有谁在等待 是否在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:25.50,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}回忆里一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:31.58,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}你流着眼泪 我说着抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:37.52,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}但我想不起 你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:43.55,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}唯一的记忆 攥在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:50.04,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(200,200)\pos(1876,40)}熟悉的文字 是你的文字
